quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  99,1,WHEN the Earth with her quaking shall quake
  99,2,And the Earth shall cast forth her burdens
  99,3,"And man shall say, What aileth her"
  99,4,On that day shall she tell out her tidings
  99,5,Because thy Lord shall have inspired her
  99,6,On that day shall men come forward in throngs to behold their works
  99,7,And whosoever shall have wrought an atom's weight of good shall behold it
  99,8,And whosoever shall have wrought an atom's weight of evil shall behold it